Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 没中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 由纪 那个难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:01:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中了 中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百万！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}天使的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吗 这就可以证明世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很忙的时候就在那里怨声载道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道女人是从来不会满足的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样不用钱就会想多吃一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再去拿一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还吃得下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是由纪请客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要吃回本 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是自助餐当然无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指这个 那些钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都是买奖券中的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就尽情的花掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是让你这么破费…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有幸福的天使在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃了二十个蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好胀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不觉得由纪最近好厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 太厉害了 运气实在太棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前根本没有觉得有过一次好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去买汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我去 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到车站体验 然后去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这主意不错 就这么决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险的 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是我一个人发穷牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你随时带着这条项链
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就随时都带给你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来…那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪 由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 可不可以给我们一些由纪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘛 也让我们感受一点幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够有这么多的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这全部都是项链的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次中特奖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 差不多一亿的头奖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你没有感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗 算是个天使吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个能够带给你幸运的人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使终于来到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是给你幸运的一种仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是最近变得比较忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是幸亏有它 是我度过充实人生的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…现在很充实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有天使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我受到那天使的宠爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上的那条项链…很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好快点丢掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是谁都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把那条项链给丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我为什么要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条项链並不像你想像中的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想夺走我的幸运 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项链是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会给别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被这项链选中的人才有資格拥有它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点都不适合这项链
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是这项链最合适的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她逃脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我想象中还要严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太巧合了 在这种地方碰见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的 这并不是巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天使赐我和他讲话的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和他讲话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我已经不再是以前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢打网球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 县大会就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是选手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了 真令人敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我对运动完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为我只有这个专长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天发生了非常棒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在电车上和那男孩讲话的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我讲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你从现在开始别再与那个男孩交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从以前就已经很仰慕他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能够第一次和他讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是你赐给我的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想夺走你的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你不要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所准备的幸福…只有你才能接触到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想失去这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信我讲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪 早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早…晨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我讲过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有它在没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条项链…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪好像太依赖那条项链了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福是要自己去争取的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 你也是妒嫉我的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奸诈狡猾之人中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你替关心 不用理我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸色不太好 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事 我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你缺少运动的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读书读得太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 听说你的成绩非常的好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…我很早就很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常常从朋友口中问你的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种四肢发达的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该不会理我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事 我非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 我可以相信这句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,项链？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮购里面那种像是护身符的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那不是那种可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有夜灵附身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 感觉到非常浓厚的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那项链的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全被夜灵给控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就不能够不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个女孩把项链给丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就得救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那也要她愿意把它丢掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道她有不能丢掉的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被眼前的幸福给迷惑着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能够接受现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无从下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫救护车！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在下面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是县大会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种样子当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的错 这是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 这全是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在讲什么 我讲过不关你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太残忍了 这样做太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所受到的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为他要夺走你的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能够保护你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后对于那些要夺走你的好运的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一直在你身边成为你的幸运天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做…这样做就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我可以得到幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那条项链丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 因为这是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在你身边的不是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是专门侵略孤独的人的心的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是利用奇怪的媚力把你给迷惑住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那不是真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的样子是丑得不能看的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它最害怕的就是你找到真正的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这样一来它就没地方可侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是我的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才能够一直是个天使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够给你幸福的只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讲得对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种幸福只不过是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且它真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要吸走你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是那夜灵做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附在你身上的夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个专门吃年轻人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是互相需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由纪 你竟然抛弃我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你 我就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一道成为天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的样子的确是很难看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 身为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为看到样子就称呼我为天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者称呼我为怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太过自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由…由纪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的欲望都是很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真有英俊的天使出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会被迷上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使和恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是哪一个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是天使了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你长得很英俊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:21:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她讲… 我想要月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不是圆圆的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是有点缺的月亮比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以戴在耳朵上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她的月亮一直都是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够看到月缺的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.32,0:23:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.59,0:23:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Night Walker 第十一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林中的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想要…什么永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波に漂う　月の光　昏睡の中　月の光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走る　独り　暗い　空を　あなたに逢えるなら
